1) create your own arch-MY_MACHINE.fcm, arch-MY_MACHINE.path and arch-MY_MACHINE.env files following the examples availables in the arch directory. Note that the arch-MY_MACHINE.env is optional
I personally used arch-X64_CURIE.fcm 

2) compile xios
./make_xios --help
./make_xios --prod --full --arch X64_CURIE --job 8 --use_oasis

-> restults of the compilation are in lib and bin directories
